ight: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px;\"><br />\r\n2012年建立电子商务平台，完善销售渠道，建立成熟的商务模式，销售量大幅度提升。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px;\"><br />\r\n2013年品牌知名度不断提升，市场份额逐步增加。公司获得&ldquo;赛富亚洲&rdquo;基金投资加盟，走上高速发展之路。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px;\"><br />\r\n2014年贝昂专业净化器品牌Airdog发布，引领品牌新起航。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>');
INSERT INTO `destoon_company_data` VALUES('4986','<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: 31px; text-align: center;\">品牌故事</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">遵化市晶海食品有限公司坐落于中国河北省遵化市地北头镇，北依长城，南临渤海，西与北京、天津接壤，东与秦皇岛相毗邻，大秦铁路穿腹而过，京沈、唐津、唐承高速路近在咫尺，交通十分便利，是中国河北生产水果罐头为主的大型食品生产加工企业。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">晶海食品公司主要生产和经营各类水果罐头，设备先进，管理科学严谨，以优等的质量和诚实的信誉打造着晶海品牌，产品赢得了消费者和经销商的认可和好评，产量逐年的稳步上升，同时公司还对外加工，现已于大连真心罐头食品公司、遵化雅山罐头食品公司有着3年的友好合作历程，现公司生产的产品已畅销全国。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;我公司地处河北老罐头加工基地唐山遵化市鲁东峪村晶海路1号，公司固定资产5000万元，&nbsp;占地面积30000平方米，现代化的生产加工车间，公司拥有职工500多人，技术人员100人，主要生产和经营各类水果罐头，从98年建厂，公司以优等的&nbsp;质量诚实的信誉打造着&ldquo;松港&rdquo;品牌，产品赢得了消费者和经销商的认可和好评，产量逐年的稳步上升。另外公司还对外加工，现已与&ldquo;大连真心罐头食品公司&rdquo;、&nbsp;&ldquo;大连头牌罐头食品公司&rdquo;有着多年的友好合作历程，现公司生产的产品已销往全国。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://wisdom.51lick.com/Public/upfile/20160516/14633899329482.png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>');
