r: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">中国第一条沙田柚深加工生产线</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">中国首家沙田柚食品现代化生产企业</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">锦香&nbsp;●&nbsp;沙田柚子茶&nbsp;●&nbsp;沙田柚果脯&nbsp;●&nbsp;柚子糕&nbsp;●&nbsp;沙田柚果肉罐头</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">广西容县锦香食品有限公司，是广西第一家目前也是华南地区最大的现代化沙田柚深加工生产基地型企业。是集研发、生产、加工、销售于一体的综合性民营农业科技型企业。公司采用沙田柚鲜果为原料、采用天然植物提取液将果皮进行去苦味、涩味，并通过特殊工艺将中国名果&mdash;&mdash;容县沙田柚开发成广西的特色休闲食品。公司生产的柚缘堂牌沙田柚子茶、果脯、果糕、水果罐头等系列休闲食品，以独特的风味，深受广大消费者的的喜爱。锦香公司做的是诚信之品，靠的是品质赢得市场，质量与科技共举，声誉与务实并进，锦香人有信心，再接再厉，展望未来，谱写光辉的美食乐章。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">沙田柚子茶（果酱）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">沙田柚子茶以蜂蜜、沙田柚鲜果为主要原料，不添加任何防腐剂、色素、甜蜜素，运用独特的配方工艺配制而成。生产的蜂蜜柚子茶产品保留了沙田柚原有的芳香及其风味特色，又不破坏原果本身所含有的各种维生素、矿物质和氨基酸等营养成分。产品口味酸甜可口，风味醇厚，颜色金黄透亮、色泽自然，是目前流行的保健食品。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">沙田柚果脯</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">容县沙田柚营养丰富、是人们喜欢吃的水果之一，也是医学界公认的最具食疗效益的水果。采用沙田柚鲜果皮、麦芽糖等蜜制而成，经过天然植物成分进行除苦处理的果脯有着柚子独特、自然的柚子芳香味、酸甜、凉润，还保留了柚子特有的柚皮甙、有机酸、维生素C、P等营养价值，绿色无添加，安全健康。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">沙田柚果糕</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">柚子果糕色泽金黄，以容县沙田柚主要原料，运用独特的配方工艺，不添加香精、香料、色素、甜蜜素，生产出来的沙田柚果糕含有丰富的维生素C和多糖，以及磷、钙、铁、钾、超纤维等对人体有益成分。保留了沙田柚原有的芳香及其风味特色，又不破坏原果本身的营养价值，而且口感津润、细腻柔软、酸甜爽口，果香四溢、芳香扑鼻，热带气息即刻溢于唇齿之间，是一种妙不可言的口味。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">容县沙田柚</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;广西容县沙田柚是我国柚类中独树一帜的优良品种，遵循土法培育，环境、气候、土壤等外界条件非常纯正，没有人为污染，沙田柚也呈自然生长状态。果形整齐、端庄，色泽艳丽，果皮细、薄，肉质细嫩、化渣，风味浓郁，味道甜中有蜜，非常可口。容县</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">沙田柚</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">营养丰富，粗蛋白质、</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">维生素C</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">含量居各种柑桔之冠，此外还含有维生素B1、B2、B6、</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">烟酸</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">和</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">磷</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">、</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">钙</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">、</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">铁</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">等，有消食、化痰、止咳、润肺、减肥、美肤养容、醒酒等功效。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">（红肉）蜜柚</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; p